'''Minister of War''' was a title used by the planets of the [[Five Worlds]] to denote their civilian [[Commander-in-Chief/Legends|commander-in-chief]].

At the start of the [[Second Galactic Civil War]], the [[Head of State/Legends|Head of State]] of [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]], [[Thrackan Sal-Solo]], deposed the previous Minister and declared himself acting Minister of War. The position may have been abolished; after Sal-Solo's death, [[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]] was made [[Supreme Commander of the Corellian Defense Force|Supreme Commander of the Corellian forces]] and [[Rorf Willems]] was made [[Minister of Defense (Five Worlds)|Minister of Defense]].

